      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个状态图来描述多人协作编辑时的文件锁定机制。核心场景是：用户打开文件后，系统要通过Ingress Controller和Load Balancer来协调锁的状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_IngressController",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer",
        "Idle"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，所以初始状态是Idle，然后由Infra_LoadBalancer触发文件打开事件？这个入口流量是由Ingress Controller接收的对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Idle",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer",
        "Infra_IngressController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Idle是初始状态。用户开始打字后进入UserAction状态，这时候系统要发起锁请求。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Idle",
        "UserAction"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我把UserAction画成\"User Edits File\"的复合状态。接下来是RequestLock状态，这里需要包含Infra_IngressController的处理逻辑。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "UserAction",
        "RequestLock",
