      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "GrantLock和DenyLock是中间状态还是事件？我看更像是请求的结果事件，直接触发状态转移。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "GrantLock",
        "DenyLock",
        "LockedState",
        "ConflictState"
