    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "你说得对，它们是转移条件。LockedState我命名为\"Locked (Infra_WorkerNode)\"，里面包含Editing子状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "LockedState",
        "Editing",
        "Infra_WorkerNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "LockedState画好了，Editing内部还需要心跳机制。每30秒发送一次Heartbeat对吧？",
